title: tab poll :flushed:
post: If you have less than 50 tabs open, click the heart emoji. If you have 50-100 tabs open, click the thumbs-up emoji. If you have 100-200 tabs open, click the crying laughing emoji. If you have 200-300 tabs open, click the shocked emoji. If you have 300-400 tabs open, click the sad emoji. If you have 400-500 tabs open, click the party popper emoji. If you have more than 500 tabs open, click the frog emoji. :frog :frog:
